original: Ljunggren, Ernst Vilhelm, ombudsman, Skövde, f. 14/11/91 i Jönköping av Nils L. o. Augusta Olsson. G. m. Sonja Rydén. Barn: Bengt f. 20, Åke 22, Ingegerd 32. — Realex. i Jönköp. 08. Anst. i Jönköp. jur. byrå 09-15, deläg. i Skövde jur. byrå fr. 21. Hob-bies: jakt, fiske.
translated: Ljunggren, Ernst Vilhelm, ombudsman, Skövde, born on November 14, 1891 in Jönköping, son of Nils L. and Augusta Olsson. Married to Sonja Rydén. Children: Bengt, born in 1920; Åke, born in 1922; Ingegerd, born in 1932. Completed Realexamen (secondary education) in Jönköping in 1908. Employed at a law office in Jönköping from 1909 to 1915, co-owner of a law office in Skövde from 1921. Hobbies: hunting, fishing. Note: '\d\d m. partners name' indicates that the person married in the year 19xx.
